flowchart LR
    DHT[DHT11<br/>Temperature and humidity] --> MCU[ATmega2560]
    CO2[CO2 sensor] --> MCU
    LIGHT[Light sensor<br/>ADC] --> MCU
    BTN1[Button 1<br/>Start/Stop session] --> MCU
    BTN2[Button 2<br/>Instant measurement] --> MCU

    MCU --> DISPLAY[Four-digit display]
    MCU --> BUZZER[Buzzer]
    MCU --> WIFI[Wi-Fi module]
    WIFI --> API[Backend API]
